                    <bibl>Morelli in <ptr target="#SECir"/>, <citedRange>258</citedRange> (no image)</bibl>, and 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#cdl2003a"/>, pp. <citedRange>220-221</citedRange> (ph.)</bibl>, whence 
